    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a brand-new demo released in January 2026, and it replaces the very dated one from 2023.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/2a4a69f6e64c887f6838eb89171006ca.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正义需要勇气。需要勇气去揭露没有人愿意面对的真相，需要勇气去直面曾经的杀人凶手——如今西装革履，手握重权受人尊敬的“普通人”，需要勇气面对威胁恐吓，孤立无援乃至更糟的境况，更需要勇气去凝视黑暗，接受被永久改变的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/3ed4e900f49a81f5cf2f36d0d89a40aa.poster.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/3ed4e900f49a81f5cf2f36d0d89a40aa.webm?t=1768243630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/3ed4e900f49a81f5cf2f36d0d89a40aa.mp4?t=1768243630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/3573c04f10c6438272b23491448153ce.avif?t=1768243630\" width=609 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是埃斯特·卡茨，一名年轻的检察官，刚加入弗里茨·鲍尔新成立的特别行动组。你的任务看似不可能完成：追查尘封多年的罪行，证据早已湮灭，证人被迫沉默，真凶却隐匿于社会最高层。你的每个决定都至关重要，每次审讯都可能离罪犯更进一步，亦或走向歧途。沉默是你最大的敌人，时间一分一秒，在你身后紧追不舍。而德国社会，这片土地和他的人民还没有做好准备，去面对过去的疮痍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/54fdbb9963de5c84ea6fbbc4e5241719.poster.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/54fdbb9963de5c84ea6fbbc4e5241719.webm?t=1768243630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/54fdbb9963de5c84ea6fbbc4e5241719.mp4?t=1768243630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/b4f6c1c429e97fe12799db634d35de42.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1956年，弗里茨·鲍尔和他的“追猎纳粹”小队在一个人人缄默只求自保的时代，力求正义降临，制裁战犯。一个检察官小队，对抗整个国家。战犯早已隐入人群，成为受尊敬的德国公民。去深入调查，过程险象环生。去揭露整个国家试图掩埋的真相，去挑战一个急于改写历史的社会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/cf4ef248b2fd7fb8daabf28d291f6a75.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入调查两起案件，基于纳粹时代发生的真实罪行改编</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >审讯证人，盘问嫌犯，打破沉默的高墙，撕开谎言的伪装</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过埃斯特的“心灵之眼”，你将见证事件的不同版本 ——证词真假难辨，真相隐于其中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零散的证据和证词中逐步拼凑出事件真相</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在法庭上，以确凿的罪名起诉罪犯，你调查的每一处细节都将面临最终考验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局由你书写：是正义审判终将降临，还是罪犯逍遥法外</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索埃斯特的故事，探寻她和家人，同事以及那位传奇人物弗里茨·鲍尔之间交织的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >置身于惊艳的赛璐珞风格3D世界，灵感源自1950年代的pulp漫画，复古风格的漫画分镜设计，重返50年代。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全英文配音精彩演绎，角色跃然眼前</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251070/extras/28787d045618f388e9caf19052f209d6.avif?t=1768243630\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p>",
